    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Role je anti-rigidní typ pro jediný princip identity, závislý na vztahu."@cs,
      "Role is an anti-rigid sortal - an individual has this type whenever it is mediated by some particular relator."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Role"@cs, "Role"@en .
  
